@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

Si Force:

I have removed all of the spam/flame posts, keep those type of posts out please. Also, Stunninhigh, I think you took too much from Jmood’s answer. I doubt he was attacking you, it’s just a way of words. Keep calm in the future please.

My post was actually helpful.

Making money in RS3 isn’t all that different from RS2. Lets say you want to make money from bossing/pvm. You can do both in RS3 and RS2. There is just a bigger variety to choose from in RS3 than in RS2. You could also try any gathering skill like woodcutting, fishing, hunter, thieving, divination, farming, etc… With farming, you can make money unless you want to get fast xp. You can’t have both. You either pick to make money or to gain fast xp.
